summary:
...DISTURBANCE IS NOT LIKELY TO BECOME A TROPICAL CYCLONE... ...BUT THE RISK OF LIFE-THREATENING FLASH FLOODING AND MUDSLIDES ACROSS JAMAICA, HISPANIOLA, AND SOUTHEASTERN CUBA CONTINUES...
